profile:
Pending Inspection Inc. a Certified Home Inspector and Certified Mold Inspector is determined to perform home inspections of the upmost quality, with integrity.  For a buyer, we make sure that you know and understand every fact about the home that you are purchasing. 

We are here to assist you in making a confident decision about your home. Whether you're buying a new property and want to be sure of what you're getting... or selling a property and want to eliminate possible problems that could delay or lose a sale. Or just want a professional to inspect and advise you on the condition and maintenance or safety recommendations of your current home.,
